"{\"uid\": \"eng.obozrevatel.com-section-war-news-zelenskyy-explains-why-initiating-a-temporary-truce-during-the-olympics-is-risky-and-why-putin-is-not-interested-in-a-dialog-17-05-2024.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"War in Ukraine  President of Ukraine Volodymyr Zelenskyy expressed skepticism about the idea of introducing aceasefireat the front during theOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9982783387382298, \"rank\": 0.0017242982247611543, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9982783387382298, \"rank\": 0.0017242982247611543, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Zelenskyy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Volodymyr Zelenskyy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Zelenskyy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Zelenskyy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the head of state, this is not effective in a fight with the Russian enemy, and the occupiers can use the ceasefire to drive tanks closer to the positions of the Defense Forces and then launch anotheroffensive.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"score\": 0.962439883394153, \"rank\": 0.022221433076230077, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zelenskyy made the statement on May 17 while talking to journalists.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In particular, he recalled that a ceasefire on the battlefield in Ukraine had already been introduced before the full-scale invasion.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9982783387382298, \"rank\": 0.0017242982247611543, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We already had a ceasefire.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it doesnot work well with this enemy.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, there is a risk: who can be sure that during the ceasefire their forces will not approach us?\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceasefire does not prevent theirequipment from moving closerand then launching an offensive.\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I do not understand the details.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, it sounds like alifeless storyto me,\\\" the president said.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ukrainian leader also spoke about how much longer the war could last.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.6603071358050672, \"rank\": 0.5115538432738287, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In particular, he noted that Russian dictatorVladimir Putinis currently not interested in a dialogue on ending the war.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"score\": 0.962439883394153, \"rank\": 0.022221433076230077, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Putin does not benefit from a dialog with the whole world becauseeven China will tell him: argue the seizure of territories.Because China stands for the territorial integrity of any state,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.897361243497506e-28, \"text\": \"Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9974038294297513, \"rank\": 0.0013211633676141797, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9974038294297513, \"rank\": 0.0013211633676141797, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zelenskyy added that today there should be grounds for Putin to look for a way out of the situation as the Kremlin leader isnot feeling uncomfortablenow.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1410, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.897361243497506e-28, \"text\": \"Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kremlin\", \"score\": 0.9633867157522236, \"rank\": 0.03800476294841356, \"text\": \"Kremlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kremlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kremlin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because where are we shooting at?\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What can we attack?\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What can we attack with?\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How much will they help us economically?Will we impose sanctions or not?\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Will there be a tribunal or not?We need to answer each of these questions.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And work and move forward in each of these areas every day,\\\" the President of Ukraine said.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1816, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9982783387382298, \"rank\": 0.0017242982247611543, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a reminder, during the year of the ceasefire in 2020-2021, according to the Ukrainian delegation of the Territorial Centres of Recruitment and Social Support,45 Ukrainian servicemenwere killed and 163 wounded in Donbas.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1910, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.